
<h1>Volunteer Today - <%= Project.latest.project_name %></h1>
<strong>You can make a difference.</strong> Experience the great feeling that comes with helping out your community. Our volunteers come to
us with all different levels of skills, and every helping hand makes a difference. Whether you're a skilled trademan or simply looking to help out
any way you can, please fill out the form below to get started.
<div style="clear:both;font-size:0em;">&nbsp;</div>	
<div class="contactform">
<form action="/contacts/create" id="new_contact" method="post">
  <%= token_tag %>

<h2>About Yourself</h2>
  <em>Bold fields are required</em><BR />
<div style="float:right; width:250px;">
  <strong>Contact Information</strong><BR />
  <ol>
    <li>
  <div class="label">Home phone </div>
  <input type="text" id="contact_home_phone" maxlength="255" name="contact[home_phone]" size="12" />
    </li><li>
  <div class="label">Work phone </div>
  <input id="contact_work_phone" maxlength="255" name="contact[work_phone]" size="12" type="text" />
  </li><li>
  <div class="label">Mobile phone </div>
  <input id="contact_mobile_phone" maxlength="255" name="contact[mobile_phone]" size="12" type="text" />
  </li></ol>
</div>

<ol>
<li class="required">
  <div class="label">First Name</div>
  <input maxlength="255" name="contact[first_name]" size="20" type="text" /></li>

<li class="required">
  <div class="label">Last Name</div>
  <input maxlength="255" name="contact[last_name]" size="20" type="text" /></li>

<li>
  <div class="label">Address 1</div>
  <input maxlength="255" name="contact[address_1]" size="30" type="text" /></li>

<li>
  <div class="label">Address 2</div>
  <input maxlength="255" name="contact[address_2]" size="30" type="text" /></li>

<li>
  <div class="label">City</div><input maxlength="255" name="contact[city]" size="20" type="text" /></li>

<li>
  <div class="label">State</div><input maxlength="2" name="contact[state]" size="5" type="text" /></li>


<li>
  <div class="label">Zip</div><input maxlength="10" name="contact[zip]" size="7" type="text" /></li>

<li>
  <div class="label">Country</div><input maxlength="255" name="contact[country]" size="20" type="text" /></li>

<li class="required">
  <div class="label">Email</div><input maxlength="255" name="contact[email]" size="40" type="text" /></li>

<h2>About Your Group</h2>				
If you are signing up as part of a group, please enter the company/group name here.
<BR /><BR />
<li>
  <div class="label" style="width: 150px;">Company Name</div><input maxlength="255" name="contact[company_name]" size="50" type="text" /></li>

<li>
  <div class="label" style="width: 150px;">Group Name </div>
  <input maxlength="255" name="groupname" size="50" type="text" /></li>

<h2>Let's Rebuild</h2>
Tell us a little bit about your skills, interests and let us know what you're thinking.
<BR /><BR />
<input name="contact[is_active]" type="hidden" value="1" />

 <div class="label" >Skills:</div>
<div style="width:350px; float:left;">
<% cnt = 0
@skills.each do |skill| %>
<input type="checkbox" name="skills" value="<%=skill.id %>" /><%= skill.description %><BR />
<% cnt+=1
if cnt > @skills.length/2
  cnt = -1000000 %>
</div>			<div style="width:350px; float:left;">
<% end %>
<% end %>
</div><div style="clear:both;font-size:0em;">&nbsp;</div>
<BR />
<li id="contact_other_skills_input">
  <div class="label" > Other Skills:</div>
  <textarea cols="40" rows="4" id="contact_other_skills" name="contact[other_skills]" rows="20"></textarea></li>

<li id="contact_comments_input">
   <div class="label" >Comments:</div>
  <textarea cols="40" rows="4" id="contact_comments" name="contact[comments]" rows="20"></textarea></li>
 <div class="label" >Interests:</div><div style="width:350px; float:left;">
<% cnt = 0
@ctypes.each do |ctype| %>
<input type="checkbox" name="ctypes" value="<%=ctype.id %>" /><%= ctype.description %><BR />
<% cnt+=1
if cnt > @ctypes.length/2
  cnt = -1000000 %>
</div>			<div style="width:350px; float:left;">
<% end %>
<% end %>
</div><div style="clear:both;font-size:1em;">&nbsp;</div>
<li><input class="create" id="contact_submit" name="commit" type="submit" value="Sign Up" /></li>
</ol>
</form>
</div>